%N A015054 Inverse of 1045th cyclotomic polynomial.
%C A015054 Periodic with period length 1045. - _Ray Chandler_, Apr 07 2017
%H A015054 Ray Chandler, <a href="/A015054/b015054.txt">Table of n, a(n) for n = 0..2000</a>
%H A015054 <a href="/index/Per#periodic">Index entries for periodic sequences</a>, period 1045.
%H A015054 <a href="/index/Rec#order_720">Index entries for linear recurrences with constant coefficients</a>, order 720.
%H A015054 <a href="/index/Pol#poly_cyclo_inv">Index to sequences related to inverse of cyclotomic polynomials</a>
%p A015054 with(numtheory,cyclotomic); c := n->series(1/cyclotomic(n,x),x,80);
%o A015054 (PARI) first(n)=Vec(1/polcyclo(1045)+O(x^(n+1))) \\ _Charles R Greathouse IV_, Jun 01 2026
